    "resumeText": "Emilio Nunez-Garcia\n\n[501-366-2080]\n\n902 N. Cascade Avenue, Colorado Springs, CO 80903\n\ne_nunezgarcia@coloradocollege.edu\n\nEducation\n\nBA Mathematical Economics 2017Colorado CollegeColorado Springs, CO\n\nProfessionalExperience\n\nCofounder, Bucketz (2016 - 2017)\n\nFounded a start-up market research recruitment firm that provides automated focus group recruitment services for mid-sized market research firms.\n\nDeveloped innovative social and search engine marketing strategy that allows firms to obtain qualified respondents for a fraction of traditional recruitment costs.\n\nDeveloped and effectively performed fundraising pitch for prospective investors.\n\nDigital Marketing Strategist, Primary Residential Mortgage Inc. (2015 - 2016)\n\nCreated and optimized digital marketing campaigns in 8 states.\n\nWorked with local insurance and real estate businesses to enhance digital networking and create effective social media marketing and brand awareness campaigns.\n\nUsed WordPress to improve SERP rank and inform webpage visitors about mortgage loans, credit scores and underwriting procedures.\n\nUsed statistical software to measure performance and optimize budget allocation.\n\nFinancial Accounting Teaching Assistant, Colorado College (2014-2015)\n\nAssisted students with homework assignments and labs in daily after-class sessions.\n\nAssisted students in one-on-one Excel and QuickBooks tutoring sessions\n\nSkills \n\nAdvanced use of Microsoft Office Suite, Stata, QuickBooks & Tableau.\n\nBilingual in English & Spanish; Proficiency in French, Italian\n\nCreative problem-solving using data based analysis\n\nExcellence in written and oral communication\n\nCertifications\n\nGoogle AdWords Fundamentals, Search and Mobile Advertising\n\nGoogle Analytics \n\nReferences\n\nAvailable upon request.\n\nhttps://www.linkedin.com/in/emilio-nunez-garcia-1a6885110",
